"title": "6232: rejection of God, results of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6232",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Rejecting God angers and grieves him. To reject God can be to reject all the benefits of the gospel, and can lead to judgment and punishment.</p>\n<h2>Rejection grieves God</h2>\n<h3>God rejected as Creator</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:6\">GEN 6:6</a></strong></p>\n<h3>God rejected as a husband</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek6:9\">EZK 6:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:2\">JER 2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:20\">JER 3:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:32\">JER 31:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos1:2\">HOS 1:2</a></p>\n<h3>God rejected as a father</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:1-Hos11:4\">HOS 11:1–11:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:18\">DEU 32:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:19\">JER 3:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:20\">JER 31:20</a></p>\n<h3>God rejected by Israel, his vineyard</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:4\">ISA 5:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:21\">JER 2:21</a></p>\n<h2>Rejection angers God and brings his wrath</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra8:22\">EZR 8:22</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:36\">JHN 3:36</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:27-Lev26:28\">LEV 26:27–26:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:16\">2CH 36:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:12\">ZEC 7:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:8\">ROM 2:8</a></p>\n<h2>The results of rejecting God</h2>\n<h3>Judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:16\">JER 1:16</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:48\">JHN 12:48</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:14-Lev26:17\">LEV 26:14–26:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps50:22\">PSA 50:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:24-Prov1:26\">PRO 1:24–1:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:22\">ISA 28:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:19\">JER 6:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:6\">JER 15:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer26:4-Jer26:6\">JER 26:4–26:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:4-Amos2:5\">AMO 2:4–2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:18-John3:19\">JHN 3:18–3:19</a></p>\n<h3>God rejects his people</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:19\">DEU 32:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:59\">PSA 78:59</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:118\">PSA 119:118</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer6:30\">JER 6:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:29\">JER 7:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos9:7\">HOS 9:7</a></p>\n<h3>God rejects those who reject him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos4:6\">HOS 4:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:33\">MAT 10:33</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:9\">LUK 12:9</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:9\">1CH 28:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr15:2\">2CH 15:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:26\">LUK 9:26</a></p>\n<h3>God hides his face</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:17-Deut31:18\">DEU 31:17–31:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:20\">DEU 32:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps88:14\">PSA 88:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:15\">ISA 1:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:4\">MIC 3:4</a></p>\n<h3>God rejects the sanctuary and its worship</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:31\">LEV 26:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:6-1Kgs9:7\">1KI 9:6–9:7</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:19-2Chr7:20\">2CH 7:19–7:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:7\">LAM 2:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek7:24\">EZK 7:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek10:18-Ezek10:19\">EZK 10:18–10:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:22-Ezek11:23\">EZK 11:22–11:23</a></p>\n<h3>God's people are removed from his presence into exile</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:18-2Kgs17:20\">2KI 17:18–17:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:23\">2KI 17:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:27\">2KI 23:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:3\">2KI 24:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:20\">2KI 24:20</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:3\">JER 52:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:15\">JER 7:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:1\">JER 15:1</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of others rejected by God</h3>\n<p>Esau:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:13\">ROM 9:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:2-Mal1:3\">MAL 1:2–1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:23\">1SA 15:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:26\">1SA 15:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:1\">1SA 16:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:15-1Sam28:16\">1SA 28:15–28:16</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:24-Jer22:25\">JER 22:24–22:25</a> <em>Jehoiachin</em></p>\n<h2>God's rejection is not final</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:44\">LEV 26:44</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:15\">ROM 11:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:22\">1SA 12:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:14\">2CH 7:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps66:20\">PSA 66:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:9\">ISA 41:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:21\">ISA 49:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa54:5-Isa54:8\">ISA 54:5–54:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:37\">JER 31:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:24-Jer33:26\">JER 33:24–33:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech10:6\">ZEC 10:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:1\">ROM 11:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:25-Rom11:29\">ROM 11:25–11:29</a></p>",
